    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a truly showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen rain or snow. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely no swirl marks or stone chips, further protected by a high-end ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the leather remains supple with no bolster wear, and all original protective films are still present on the infotainment screens. Mechanically, the car is flawless, backed by a comprehensive folder of dealership service records and a clean history. This is a rare opportunity to own a 'wrapper' condition vehicle that looks, smells, and drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line.",
      "price": 48500.0,
